{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871909881,"sessionID":"ses_285cbe021ffeZvmscYEM4Pid5B","part":{"id":"prt_d7a342d70001MRiuUWVYMFtf3f","messageID":"msg_d7a3420d0001yEGgqvPC8OmvO6","sessionID":"ses_285cbe021ffeZvmscYEM4Pid5B","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_cb0a0fbc80c646a4be44afcb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure (top-level directories and key files)\n2. Any Helm chart related files (look for Chart.yaml, values.yaml, templates/, helm/, charts/, manifests/ directories)\n3. Any spec documents related to AR-030 or Helm charts\n4. Any test files related to Helm charts or manifests\n5. Any documentation about the project's architecture or requirements\n\nSearch very thoroughly - check all directories, look for .yaml, .yml, .md files that might contain specs or requirements. Also look for any BACKLOG, specs/, docs/, requirements/ directories.\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of what you find, including file paths and key content.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_285cbc05cffe2TebHSvmhgBYix (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is the full summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Summary: AgentCube Project\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\n**Repository:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`  \n**Purpose:** A Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n**Top-level directories and key files:**\n\n| Path | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `agentd` | Binary (idle cleanup controller) |\n| `changes/` | 30 change requests (AR-001 through AR-030), each with proposal.md, design.md, delta-spec.md, tasks.md |\n| `ci-cd/` | CI/CD spec and design (GitHub Actions workflows) |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | CLI tooling specs |\n| `client-go/` | Generated Kubernetes client code for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` |\n| `cmd/` | Go binaries: `agentd/main.go`, `workloadmanager/main.go`, `picod/main.go` |\n| `code-execution/` | Code execution specs |\n| `coverage.out` | Go test coverage output |\n| `delta-spec.md` | AR-029: SDK HTTP underlying client delta spec |\n| `deployment/` | Deployment spec, design, and client-go documentation |\n| `design.md` | AR-029: SDK HTTP client layer design |\n| `go.mod` | Go module: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`, Go 1.25.0 |\n| `go.sum` | Go dependency checksums |\n| `idle-cleanup/` | Idle cleanup spec and design |\n| `integrations/` | Dify plugin and PCAP analyzer specs and designs |\n| `manifests/` | Helm chart (`charts/base/`) |\n| `pkg/` | Go packages |\n| `project.md` | Project context document |\n| `proposal.md` | AR-028: SDK AgentRuntimeClient proposal |\n| `python-sdk/` | Python SDK (`agentcube/`) with tests |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | Sandbox orchestration specs |\n| `session-routing/` | Session routing spec and design |\n| `session-store/` | Session store specs |\n| `tasks.md` | AR-023: CLI invoke/status commands tasks |\n| `test_spec.md` | TDD specification for test cases |\n| `test/` | E2E tests and Helm chart tests |\n| `testing/` | TDD manifest |\n\n**Tech Stack:**\n- **Server:** Go 1.24/1.25, Gin HTTP framework\n- **CLI/SDK:** Python >= 3.10, Typer (CLI), FastAPI (examples)\n- **Kubernetes:** CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, agent-sandbox\n- **Storage:** Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go)\n- **Auth:** JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview\n- **Packaging:** Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD\n\n---\n\n### 2. Helm Chart Files\n\nThe Helm chart exists at `manifests/charts/base/` with the following structure:\n\n| File | Absolute Path | Description |\n|------|---------------|-------------|\n| **Chart.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` | Chart metadata: `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, `appVersion: 1.0.0` |\n| **values.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | Default values for all components (65 lines): Redis, Router, Workload Manager, Volcano scheduler |\n| **_helpers.tpl** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` | Naming helper functions |\n| **workloadmanager.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | WM Deployment + Service |\n| **agentcube-router.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | Router Deployment + Service |\n| **rbac/workloadmanager.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | WM ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding |\n| **rbac-router.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Optional Router RBAC (gated by `router.rbac.create`) |\n| **volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Optional Volcano scheduler (gated by `volcano.scheduler.enabled`) |\n| **CRD: AgentRuntime** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced) |\n| **CRD: CodeInterpreter** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced) |\n\n**Key values.yaml defaults:**\n- `redis.addr: \"\"`, `redis.password: \"\"` (must be provided at install time)\n- `router.replicas: 1`, image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router:latest`, port 8080\n- `workloadmanager.replicas: 1`, image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest`, port 8080\n- `volcano.scheduler.enabled: false`, image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler:latest`\n- Resources: limits `cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi`, requests `cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi`\n\n---\n\n### 3. AR-030 Spec Documents (Helm Chart Templates & Values)\n\nAR-030 is the change request specifically for the Helm chart. All four documents are located at:\n\n| Document | Absolute Path | Lines | Content |\n|----------|---------------|-------|---------|\n| **proposal.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md` | 117 | Purpose, scope (in/out), architecture summary, impact analysis, alternatives considered, upstream dependencies |\n| **design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md` | 798 | Full architecture, data structures (values.yaml key tree, template variable mapping, RBAC rules, CRD definitions, Volcano ConfigMap), API contracts (install commands, namespace scoping, naming conventions), error handling, testing strategy, implementation steps, follow-up changes |\n| **delta-spec.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md` |